748
00:53:48,020 --> 00:53:49,149
I'll be off now.

749
00:53:53,089 --> 00:53:54,120
See you later.

750
00:53:55,359 --> 00:53:56,359
Su Ryeon.

751
00:54:01,770 --> 00:54:02,870
